added.title: Vote Zombozo!
added.description: When the Rustbucket must tune-up in the same town as Zombozo's latest campaign trail stop, Ben soon discovers the clown is using his speeches to hypnotize then rob the town, and Team Tennyson must stop the baddie from winning the election.

added.title: Safari Sa'Bad
added.description: On their trip to Adrenaworld West, Ben takes a detour on a jungle cruise and finds himself hunted by the evil Tim Buktu. Our hero must outwit the baddie if he wants to make it off the amusement park ride alive!

added.title: The Nature of Things
added.description: While sightseeing at the Geyser Gulch National Park, the Tennyson trio uncover Steam Smythe's steam-powered generator and must shut it down before it overloads the power grid or, even worse, causes a massive earthquake that destroys the entire park!

added.title: The Sound and the Furry
added.description: As Team Tennyson leaves the Frozen Man Festival, Lord Decibel takes center stage to threaten the festival-goers, creating an avalanche if his ransom isn't paid. An over matched Ben must step out of his comfort zone to save the festival from his noisy nemesis!

added.title: Reststop Roustabout
added.description: With the Rustbucket stopped on the Midwest roadside, Ben locks himself inside with his tablet as Max and Gwen enjoy the great outdoors, until Team Tennyson is pulled into a wild Jack-a-Lope chase.

added.title: That's the Stuff
added.description: While touring a space museum, Ben's excitement multiplies when he learns that recently discovered space stuff is being examined inside the museum's lab. Once the stuff comes to life and the shape-shifting goo replicates our hero, Ben must look within if he is to stop the case of mistaken identity.

added.title: The Feels
added.description: While Max and Gwen revel in the holiday spirit of Winter Wonderland, Ben couldn't be more unamused and focused on the toys, but once the Weatherheads set their sights on Winter Wonderland as their next target, our hero must become one with his emotion if he is to save the town.

added.title: Past Aliens Present
added.description: After Ben stumbles upon a video of Cannonbolt ripping up a computer lab on the internet, Team Tennyson must race to State U to find the imposter; but once Ben discovers it is a steam-punk version of his alien that is terrorizing the campus, Ben must take down the man behind the machine, Steam Smythe!

added.title: Dreamtime
added.description: After a series of reoccurring nightmares affect his sleep, Ben refuses to open up to Max and Gwen about what's bothering him, but once they realize Zombozo himself is behind it, Ben must accept Max and Gwen's help if they are going to put a stop to the terror.

added.title: The Future is Cardboard
added.description: The kids meet an eccentric Cardboard Creator that invites Craig to help finish his masterpiece.

added.title: The Invitation
added.description: Craig and his friends are invited to an exclusive tea party with delicious desserts, if they can last to the end of the party…

added.title: Wisdom, Strength, and Charisma
added.description: When Enid goes to a new school, KO sets out to make sure she fits in.

added.title: Space Race
added.description: With Clarence distracted by the mysterious power of the moon, his class competes to build the highest-flying rocket. Will Sumo's homemade bucket of bolts beat Belson's store-bought rocket?

added.title: The Ultimate Adventure: Come Along with Me
added.description: The fate of Ooo is revealed to two adventurers in the distant future. Princess Bubblegum gathers her allies while Finn searches for a way to prevent the coming Great Gum War.

added.title: Dream of Love Music Video
added.description: Be prepared to be serenaded by the sweet, sweet sounds of Tree Trunks and Mr. Pig.

added.title: Slow Dance with You Music Video
added.description: Marceline performs a new song at her solo concert!

added.title: Simon and Marcy's Origin Story
added.description: 996 years ago, a man named Simon Petrikov met a little girl named Marceline at the end of the Great Mushroom War, and they became great friends.

added.title: Trash Cat
added.description: Uncle Grandpa helps a cat who's afraid to take baths.

added.title: Yo soy Polar
added.description: Cuando Polar se golpea la cabeza, Pardo y Panda se dan cuenta de que su comportamiento cambia.

added.title: Saca tu Bestia
added.description: Craig quiere jugar a un popular juego de cartas, así que decide tomar prestadas las cartas antiguas y valiosas de Bernard.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: El futuro es de Carton
added.description: Los niños conocen a un excéntrico Creador de Cartón que invita a Craig a ayudarlo a terminar su obra maestra.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Opposites Attract
added.description: Fire Man and Wave Man team up to evaporate the city's water supply, forcing Mega Man to team up with an ally of his own- Suna.

added.title: I.C.E. (In Case of Emergency)
added.description: When Ice Man decides to be a hero, Mega Man, influenced by Ice Man's literalness, steps down from the hero biz until a true crisis snaps him out of it.

added.title: Trust Your Guts, Man!
added.description: Guts Man tries to undo Dr. Light's eco-friendly disposal of trash in Silicon City by infiltrating the family and destroying the Lighthouse so he can eat it!

added.title: La Traes
added.description: Un despiadado juego de persecución desata un caos en el Arroyo, y se declara a Kelsey como la próxima perseguidora.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: El Libro Final
added.description: El último libro de fantasía de la serie favorita de Kelsey desaparece de la biblioteca. Por eso, Craig decide ayudarla a resolver el misterio de quién se lo llevó.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Salvajessa
added.description: Un encuentro con Salvajessa, guardiana de la naturaleza, inspira a Kelsey a dedicarse a una causa.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Escape de la Cena Familiar
added.description: En el arroyo se disputa una enorme pelea con globos acuáticos, pero Craig está atrapado en la cena familiar, a menos que pueda escapar.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Demasiados Unikitties
added.description: Unikitty llega a la conclusión de que todo el mundo sería mucho más feliz si pensara como ella, iy tal vez pueda lograrlo con la ayuda de la Dra. Fox! Unikitty copia sus ondas cerebrales en todos sus amigos y los Unikittyfica, para que todos puedan ser siempre positivos. Pero pronto, Unikitty se da cuenta de que puede haber un exceso de "buena princesa".

added.title: Festival de Cine
added.description: iEs la noche del estreno en el Festival de Cine de Unireino! Todo el mundo está entusiasmado por ver lo que hicieron los amigos, especialmente Richard, que se considera el máximo experto en cine y no puede esperar a destrozar todas las películas de los demás. Pero después de interpretar el papel del crítico, ¿será la película de Rick una obra maestra o un fracaso?

added.title: Monstruo en el Jardin
added.description: Craig está decidido a atrapar al monstruo que ha estado desatando un caos en el jardín del abuelo.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Demasiados Tesoros
added.description: Con la esperanza de reparar su fuerte, Craig consigue la ayuda de Los Veloces Diez para llevarlos hasta la legendaria pila de basura.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol
